
What is Build:
---------------
	- build is nothing but creating the package
	- build means converting your source code into a runnable application

	Example:
		- your write java code	-- .java files
		- build tool converts it into -- .jar or .war file

		it includes:
			compiling code
			resolving dependencies
			packaging (creating deployable files)
			(Code -> Compile -> Package -> Output file (jar/war))